title: Duke Dudes Paolo Banchero and AJ Griffin
description:
J. Kyle Mann and Jonathan Tjarks return to discuss young prospect Paolo Banchero, how size and defense can be a well-developed asset for a young college player, and what comparable players like AJ Griffin can do.
Hosts: J. Kyle Mann and Jonathan Tjarks
Producer: Steve Ahlman
